01:36:06.427 --> 01:36:08.511
(cries out)

01:36:59.897 --> 01:37:01.773
Carolina.

01:37:01.857 --> 01:37:03.733
Roberto.

01:37:25.256 --> 01:37:31.845
(man) What did you want
from these people? I ask you again.

01:37:32.179 --> 01:37:35.223
What did you want from these people?

01:37:36.809 --> 01:37:39.310
Nothing. They were friends.

01:37:43.357 --> 01:37:45.441
Friends?

01:37:48.737 --> 01:37:51.030
We had dinner there.

01:37:52.116 --> 01:37:56.494
Why did you go back with your boyfriend
to these people?

01:37:57.413 --> 01:38:00.248
What did you want from them?

01:38:04.295 --> 01:38:07.505
Did your boyfriend like the woman?

01:38:09.758 --> 01:38:12.886
I liked her. I don't think that he...

01:38:14.346 --> 01:38:17.432
Did your boyfriend like the man?

01:38:18.350 --> 01:38:20.852
No. No, he didn't.

01:38:20.936 --> 01:38:23.104
And you?

01:38:23.606 --> 01:38:25.773
You liked the man?

01:38:25.858 --> 01:38:29.319
- Did you like the man?
- No.

01:38:29.403 --> 01:38:35.366
So, why did you go to dinner?
And why did you go back?

01:38:35.451 --> 01:38:40.038
Why did you come to Venice?
What were you looking for?

01:38:40.789 --> 01:38:46.044
- Nothing, we ju...
- Were you looking for... some fun?

01:38:48.964 --> 01:38:51.049
We were...

01:38:53.844 --> 01:38:56.554
We were going to get married.

01:39:04.813 --> 01:39:07.565
Is this the body of Colin Mayhew?

01:39:10.861 --> 01:39:12.946
Sign here.

01:39:23.832 --> 01:39:27.251
- Combed his hair the wrong way.
- Sorry?

01:39:29.129 --> 01:39:31.422
It doesn't go this way.

01:39:38.263 --> 01:39:40.348
It goes this way.

01:40:46.331 --> 01:40:50.418
...a tourist, but now
you plan everything in advance.

01:40:50.502 --> 01:40:56.132
You sell your bar, you sell your apartment,
you buy drug, and so on and so on.

01:40:56.216 --> 01:41:00.511
And then on the other hand you leave
your razor with your fingerprints,

01:41:00.596 --> 01:41:07.226
you book a ticket under your own name
and you travel with your own passport.

01:41:07.311 --> 01:41:09.270
We don't get it.

01:41:09.354 --> 01:41:12.148
Listen. Let me tell you something.

01:41:12.232 --> 01:41:16.527
My father was a very big man.

01:41:17.571 --> 01:41:21.491
All his life he wore a black moustache.

01:41:21.575 --> 01:41:25.870
When it turned grey
he used a little brush to keep it black,

01:41:25.954 --> 01:41:29.457
such as ladies use for their eyes.

01:41:29.541 --> 01:41:31.626
Mascara.
